Class SequenceVectors<T extends SequenceElement>

  • java.lang.Object

    public class SequenceVectors<T extends SequenceElement>
extends WordVectorsImpl<T>
implements WordVectors
    SequenceVectors implements abstract features extraction for Sequences and SequenceElements, using SkipGram, CBOW or DBOW (for Sequence features extraction).
